            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>creamy vegetable stock</strong> and <strong>gnocchi</strong> to the pot with the softened mushrooms<strong> </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 7-8 min, or until the liquid has started to thicken and the gnocchi is cooked through</p>",
