      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>butter</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>basa</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side, or until browned and cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
